'''卓木拉日峰'''也作'''绰莫拉日峰'''（{{bo|z=ཇོ་མོ་ལྷ་རི|w=jo mo lha ri|p=Qomo Lhari}}）位于[[中国|中国]]与[[不丹|不丹]]的边境上，最高点海拔7326米<ref>另有“7314米、7350米”等说法</ref>，为不丹的第二高峰。山名意为“[[干城章嘉峰|干城章嘉]]的新娘”，也叫“王妃神山”。卓木拉日峰顶峰突兀，壁峭坡陡，峰顶气候恶劣，登山难度极大<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 户外资料网 | title = 绰莫拉日峰 | url = http://www.8264.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=848389 | date =  | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204061341/http://www.8264.com/shanfeng-848389 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1937年由一支[[英国|英国]]探险队完成首登<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = www.summitpost.org | title = Chomolhari | url = http://www.summitpost.org/chomolhari/358481 | date =  | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204061352/https://www.summitpost.org/chomolhari/358481 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
